    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Affordable and dependable daily driver ready for its next chapter! This vehicle runs and drives reliably, making it a great pick for buyers seeking practical transportation at a budget-friendly price. It does show its age with some visible wear and cosmetic imperfections, so what you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises. If you're looking for a straightforward, functional ride without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look!",
