    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Reliable & Well-Maintained \u2014 A Solid Good Condition Value! This car is a fantastic everyday driver that has been well cared for and is ready to serve its next owner with confidence! The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic blemishes you'd expect from normal use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and handles well \u2014 this is a car you can depend on without worry. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle that delivers great value without the premium price of a mint-condition car, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 a solid option for buyers looking for reliable everyday transportation without paying premium prices. The car starts and runs consistently, and while it shows its age with some cosmetic wear and minor mechanical quirks, it is fundamentally sound and road-worthy. Expect some visible wear on the interior and exterior \u2014 think scuffs, light scratches, or faded trim \u2014 and possibly a few minor issues that a competent mechanic could address without breaking the bank. It won't win any beauty contests, but it will get you where you need to go day in and day out. A good choice for a practical buyer who wants dependable transportation at a fair price.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Solid & Honest \u2014 A Fair-Condition Car at a Fair Price!** Here's a vehicle that gives you real, everyday transportation without the premium price tag! This car is in fair condition \u2014 it has some wear and minor imperfections that come with age and use, but it's a functional, drivable vehicle that can serve you well. You'll want to budget for some maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups down the road, but there's nothing here we're hiding. If you're looking for honest, dependable transportation at a reasonable price, this could be exactly what you need \u2014 come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 a functional, drivable car that shows its age and use but remains a viable option for budget-conscious buyers willing to accept some imperfections. The exterior displays noticeable wear, including several scratches, minor dents, and areas where the paint has faded or chipped, giving the body a tired appearance. The interior is similarly worn, with visible scuffs on the trim, some fraying on the upholstery, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but prospective buyers should be aware that it may require some attention in the near term \u2014 routine maintenance items are likely overdue, and there may be minor mechanical quirks that a pre-purchase inspection would reveal. This is not a turn-key, worry-free vehicle, but with some investment of time and money, it can serve as reliable everyday transportation. Ideal for a buyer comfortable with a project or someone who simply needs affordable mobility and understands the trade-offs involved.",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $20,000, a price that honestly reflects its fair condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car is functional and drivable, but it shows its age and use in several ways. You can expect visible wear on the interior surfaces, including some scuffs, fading, or minor tears on the upholstery. The exterior has noticeable scratches, small dents, or paint imperfections that are visible upon close inspection. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but there may be some components that are not in peak condition \u2014 minor issues such as slightly worn brakes, aging belts or hoses, or a suspension that isn't as tight as it once was. It has not been in any major accidents to our knowledge, but it has lived a normal, well-used life. This is a solid choice for a buyer who needs reliable transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that may require some maintenance attention in the near term. A pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly encouraged, and we welcome any questions about the car's history.",
      "price": 20000.0,
